###########
########### Working tor configuration tested with Raspberry pi 2 B
########### Tor working as a Transparent Proxy with iptables so all traffic of our box is redirected to tor network to anonymize the user




Log notice file /var/log/tor/notices.log
VirtualAddrNetwork 10.192.0.0/10
AutomapHostsSuffixes .onion,.exit
AutomapHostsOnResolve 1
TransPort 9040
TransListenAddress 192.168.42.1 #Our hostapd and isc-dhcp-server ip address
DNSPort 53
DNSListenAddress 192.168.42.1 # Same




